text: Sheean is a surname and may refer to: *Teddy Sheean (1923–1942), sailor in the Royal Australian Navy *Vincent Sheean (1899–1975), American journalist and novelist *HMAS Sheean (SSG 77), fifth of six Collins-class submarines operated by the Royal Australian Navy *Diana Forbes-Robertson, also known as Diana Sheean, wife of Vincent Sheean (1915–1987), British writer
title: Sheean
